# Cursor Rules - TestTDD
 
## React & JSX Stability
- Maintain strict order of variable and hook definitions.
- Always verify JSX tag balancing in large components like App.jsx.
- Prevent Circular dependencies and Reference Errors.
 
## UI/UX Standards
- Use HSL based color palettes.
- Apply glassmorphism and modern shadows.
- Ensure Dark Mode compatibility.
 
## Agent Guidelines
- Read .agent/rules.md for detailed architectural constraints.
- Prioritize concise edits to avoid code corruption.
